column14: Apple Ipad 5 India | Apple Ipad 5 Expected Price  |  Apple Ipad 5 Release Date
column15: Ipad 5 is expected to release in the mids of 2013. Check out for the price and features of the all new Apple Ipad 5.
column17:
The iPad admirers are unable to wait more to get their hands on Apple iPad 5 and to bring ecstasy to them the rumors about Apple iPad 5 release date has already hit the web world. If rumors are to be believed  iPad 5 will release in September 2013. Though it’s a long wait for keen buyers but it is worth waiting.

As per the rumors the look of Apple iPad 5 will be completely astonishing with a mix design of iPad mini and iPhone 5. It will be a heavily revised device with a flat back brushed aluminium finish and possibly available in black and white colour. Is your heart beating fast getting the details of the most awaited device i.e. Apple iPad 5? Well it is ought to be!

On one hand there are many rumors about the look of iPad 5 but on the other hand there is no talk about the specifications. However there is no need to get disheartened as undoubtedly iPad 5 will be somehow advanced than iPad 4  iPad 3  iPad 2 and iPad. After all these products are Apple’s creation! They keep the essence maintained but always come out updated than their former ones.

The Ipad 5 features - Thin In Size & GF2 touchscreen technology.


Status- Rumor Expected Price- N/A

column14: Apple iphone 6 Features | Apple Iphone 6 India | Apple Iphone Release Date
column15: Checkout the all new Apple Iphone 6 features  price  release date in India. Soon Iphone 6 rumors will be taking shape.
column17:
Let’s begin cheering for Apple iPhone 6 which is expected to hit Indian market next year. Just after the arrival of Apple iPhone 5 eyes with keenness started looking for iPhone 6. The excitement of people knows no bounds. To instigate more excitement let’s move forward on a voyage to talk about Apple iPhone 6.

Apple has never experimented with the size of screen in iPhones but you can expect a change in the screen size with iPhone 6. If iphone 6 rumors are to be believed a larger screen will replace the conventional screen of iPhones. To stay competitive Apple may find the need to expand its screen size. Realizing the interest of people for larger than 4-inch screen Apple possibly stop sticking to its one-handed phone design.

When it’s Apple genuineness is always expected. Apple’s products are admired for their quality consistency and simplicity. They don’t give a wide choice to customers in order to save them from confusion but what they deliver is always of unmatched quality. That’s what expected from iPhone 6 as well.

With fingers crossed we can only hope for better than earlier product. As Apple believes "we know better" we hope they continue to know better and also come up with better.

The phone features-

Curved screen

p-Si LCD Screen

Wireless Charging

Projector in iPhone 6

128 GB Storage


Apple Iphone 6 is expected soon   Expected Price- Rs 60000.
